{"tid":1778124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DGX 我覺得首國歌同進行曲可以進一步加長","createTime":"2019-12-10T16:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T08:07:55.000Z","uid":251732,"like":14,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0398d3459c413e00ff94ef28bb75ca590394ce41","tid":1778124,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"參考返其他主要國家嘅成句國歌歌詞， 如果首歌加多兩三段嘅新歌詞段落嘅話， 咁就可以令成首歌睇落去真係好似一首歌咁可以長唱兩三段。<br />\n<br />\n例如美國同南韓國歌， 其實正式嘅國歌係有兩三段<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kpImRb5hvKw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkpImRb5hvKw&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=e1babcc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kpImRb5hvKw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TGOPzKh7jVQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTGOPzKh7jVQ&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=c3632d22\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TGOPzKh7jVQ</a><br />\n<br />\n所以小弟心喐喐喺不屈進行曲嗰度加多一段歌詞， 希望團隊可以加以參考或修改，甚至乎可以考慮幫願榮光歸香港加多兩三段歌詞<br />\n<br />\n 第一版本 第二段歌詞:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">來前行 戰鬥吧<br />\n戰地上 不死的身<br />\n高舉鐵桿 即使艱辛<br />\n去剿滅 屠夫 與叛徒<br />\n<br />\n在籠牢下  你受夠嗎<br />\n在砲火裏 不惜犧牲 <br />\n告眾烈士不死的你 <br />\n去創建明天的香港<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n尾嗰段照舊，可以做副歌詞<br />\n<br />\n為大義 來一起奮抗戰<br />\n讓熱淚 和鮮血 沒白掉<br />\n銘記 眾同伴獻身 約誓<br />\n<br />\n願萬代 仍堅守這要塞<br />\n讓願望 能歸依這家邦<br />\n在 絕地 屹立 共建光輝<br />\n將正義 歸萬眾<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4hkMgPfIpjo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4hkMgPfIpjo&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=9a991b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4hkMgPfIpjo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n沒有暴徒只有暴政<br />\n解散狗隊刻不容緩<br />\n天滅中共全黨死清光</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5578f252a71ab184d8d1c16d08262fc2160c8f2d","tid":1778124,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"不忘被捕手足！！！！<br />\n幫手入黎推plz<br />\n<br />\n我地真係唔可以當被補既手足係condom<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778111</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35a0abae388b8316f3fce9af5388c0adb54b6abc","tid":1778124,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5578f252a71ab184d8d1c16d08262fc2160c8f2d","tid":1778124,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"不忘被捕手足！！！！<br />\n幫手入黎推plz<br />\n<br />\n我地真係唔可以當被補既手足係condom<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778111</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:46:27.000Z","msg":"push ah <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8da34e00933daf23822c97f53bd38446794af3b","tid":1778124,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:46:44.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"70cff268b62f75fa5f1d3db72a3d78f8eb1b0907","tid":1778124,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"e21a77763e17ab5fac71abd0f817cc1ec7b0a40d","tid":1778124,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a0abae388b8316f3fce9af5388c0adb54b6abc","tid":1778124,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5578f252a71ab184d8d1c16d08262fc2160c8f2d","tid":1778124,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"不忘被捕手足！！！！<br />\n幫手入黎推plz<br />\n<br />\n我地真係唔可以當被補既手足係condom<br />\n<a href=\"https:/